{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e41f2b4d2a","title":"给刘松林的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"75f8cecffc","index":0,"year":1957,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"04da7e0201","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘松林，原名刘思齐，1949年10月同毛泽东之子毛岸英结婚。1950年11月毛岸英在抗美援朝战争中辆鞋。1955年刘松林去苏联，在莫斯科大学数力系读书。1957年暑假回国办理转学手续。同年10月转入北京大学俄罗斯语言文学系读书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"63630c79d5","type":"title","text":"给刘松林的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"},{"id":"04da7e0201","type":"paragraph","text":"思齐儿：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"},{"id":"635378cbdf","type":"paragraph","text":"信收到。回来了，很高兴。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"},{"id":"5434175e4d","type":"paragraph","text":"转学事是好的，自己作主，向组织申请，得允即可。如不得允，仍去苏联，改学文科，时间长一点也不要紧。不论怎样，都要自己作主，不要用家长的名义去申请，注意为盼。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"},{"id":"0b8740d378","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你进步","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"},{"id":"82a9c06d39","type":"paragraph","text":"父亲","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"},{"id":"9153aab180","type":"paragraph","text":"八月四日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a"}],"page":{"id":"eb0d22c21c","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"e41f2b4d2a","start":201,"end":201}}}},"__N_SSG":true}